<p><span><span>1、根据世卫组织最新实时统计数据，截至欧洲中部时间</span>12<span>月</span><span>14</span><span>日</span><span>18</span><span>时</span><span>23</span><span>分（北京时间</span><span>12</span><span>月</span><span>15</span><span>日</span><span>1</span><span>时</span><span>23</span><span>分），全球累计新冠肺炎确诊病例</span><span>71051805</span><span>例，累计死亡病例</span><span>1608648</span><span>例。</span><span>14</span><span>日全球新冠肺炎确诊病例新增</span><span>574969</span><span>例，死亡病例新增</span><span>8726</span><span>例。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>2、约翰斯</span>·霍普金斯大学统计数据显示，截至美国东部时间<span>12</span><span>月</span><span>14</span><span>日</span><span>15</span><span>时</span><span>55</span><span>分，美国新冠肺炎确诊病例超过</span><span>1638</span><span>万例，达</span><span>16388504</span><span>例，死亡病例超过</span><span>30</span><span>万例，达</span><span>300267</span><span>例。</span></span></p>
